  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the therapeutic effectiveness and cost-effectivity
      of pharmaceutical care for diabetes type 2 patients. Patients will be randomly allocated to
      the control group ( = no input from pharmacist) or intervention group ( = with pharmaceutical
      care at baseline and follow-up visits over 6 months).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
