  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  45-75 years

          -  Body Mass Index &gt;= 25

          -  Diabetes treatment for at least 12 months

          -  Regular visitors of the participating community pharmacy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients taking only insulin (no oral antidiabetic drugs)
      </textblock>
